text: Ioana Ducu and Ioana Loredana Roșca were the defending champions, but were not eligible to participate this year. Miriam Kolodziejová and Markéta Vondroušová won the title, defeating Caroline Dolehide and Katerina Stewart in the final, 6–0, 6–3. == Seeds == == Draw == === Finals === === Top half === === Bottom half === == External links == * Draw Girls' Doubles French Open, 2015 Girls' Doubles
